1. *Pratim* njene postupke sa velikim interesovanjem. (I am following her actions with great interest.)
2. *Pratim* sve novosti iz političke sfere. (I am following all the news from the political sphere.)
3. Moj prijatelj *prati* najnovije trendove u modi. (My friend is following the latest fashion trends.)
4. Moja majka *prati* sve informacije o zdravlju. (My mother is following all the information about health.)
5. *Prati* li ona dešavanja u svetu? (Is she following the events in the world?)
6. *Pratim* svoje snove dok ih realizujem. (I am following my dreams while realizing them.)